modelVersions.name: Ichihime ( ? in 1 )
modelVersions.description:
Ichihime 一姬

Trigger word are "Majsoul,Ichihime,Ichihime_*”， Ichihime_* stands for these clothes:

触发词是： "Majsoul,Ichihime,Ichihime_*”，其中 Ichihime_* 要换成下列之一：

  • Ichihime_original : Original costume （原皮）

  • Ichihime_kimono : the second kimono costume，the side-view one with red kimono （婚皮）

  • Ichihime_newyear：the New-year themed long red kimono costume.（新年皮肤）

  • Ichihime_swimsuit：the swimsuit costume （泳装皮肤）

Since lots of Ichihime's costumes are kimono, it's possible that the result will have some cross-overs, try to use more prompts to describe the costume.

When you're not using these clothes, just use "Majsoul,Ichihime".

当你不画上面这些衣服的时候，只用前两个触发词。
